&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/cc879317.aspx&quot;&gt;Optimizing MERGE Statement Performance&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
